Class ItemComparison

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.CoreItemComparison
      • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.ItemComparison
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EntityComparison, LinkComparison

    public abstract class ItemComparison
extends CoreItemComparison
    A representation of the differences between two versions of the same Item.
    Since:
    2.0

    • Constructor Detail

      • ItemComparison

        protected ItemComparison(CoreItem olderItem,
                         CoreItem newerItem,
                         boolean deletionChanged,
                         boolean securityChanged,
                         boolean primaryPropertiesChanged,
                         boolean modifiedTimestampChanged,
                         Collection<String> addedCardIds,
                         Collection<String> removedCardIds,
                         Collection<SourceInfoComparison> changedSourceInfos,
                         Collection<CardComparison> changedCards,
                         Collection<String> addedPropertyGroupIds,
                         Collection<String> removedPropertyGroupIds,
                         Collection<String> addedPropertyIds,
                         Collection<String> removedPropertyIds,
                         Collection<String> changedPropertyIds)
        Constructs a new ItemComparison.
        Parameters:
        olderItem - The older Item in this ItemComparison.
        newerItem - The newer Item in this ItemComparison.
        deletionChanged - true if one of the Item versions is marked as deleted while the other is not; false otherwise.
        securityChanged - true if the Item versions have different security settings; false otherwise.
        primaryPropertiesChanged - true if the Item versions have different primary properties; false otherwise.
        modifiedTimestampChanged - true if the Item versions have different modified timestamps; false otherwise.
        addedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the newer but not the older Item.
        removedCardIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the older but not the newer Item.
        changedSourceInfos - SourceInfoComparisons describing SourceInfo changes between Cards present on both Items.
        changedCards - CardComparisons describing changes between Cards present on both Items.
        addedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the newer but not the older Item.
        removedPropertyGroupIds - Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the older but not the newer Item.
        addedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the newer but not the older Item.
        removedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the older but not the newer Item.
        changedPropertyIds - Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys whose values are different in the two Items.

    • Method Detail

      • isModifiedTimestampChanged

        public final boolean isModifiedTimestampChanged()
        Indicates whether there is a difference between the modified timestamps of the older and newer Items.
        Returns:
        true if the Item versions have different modified timestamps; false otherwise.

      • getAddedCardIds

        public final Collection<String> getAddedCardIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the newer but not the older Item.

        Note: When a Card has been added, getAddedPropertyIds() and getAddedPropertyGroupIds() do not return information about the contents of that Card.

        Returns:
        See above.

      • getRemovedCardIds

        public final Collection<String> getRemovedCardIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of Cards present on the older but not the newer Item.

        Note: When a Card has been removed, getRemovedPropertyIds() and getRemovedPropertyGroupIds() do not return information about the contents of that Card.

        Returns:
        See above.

        public final Collection<SourceInfoComparison> getChangedSourceInfos()

        Returns:
        See above.

        public final Collection<CardComparison> getChangedCards()
        Gets CardComparisons describing changes between Cards present on both Items.
        Returns:
        See above.

      • getAddedPropertyGroupIds

        public final Collection<String> getAddedPropertyGroupIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the newer but not the older Item.
        Returns:
        See above, but note that identifiers are not returned for PropertyGroups in added Cards.

      • getRemovedPropertyGroupIds

        public final Collection<String> getRemovedPropertyGroupIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of PropertyGroups present on the older but not the newer Item.
        Returns:
        See above, but note that identifiers are not returned for PropertyGroups in removed Cards.

      • getAddedPropertyIds

        public final Collection<String> getAddedPropertyIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the newer but not the older Item.
        Returns:
        See above, but note that identifiers are not returned for Propertys in added PropertyGroups, or in added Cards.

      • getRemovedPropertyIds

        public final Collection<String> getRemovedPropertyIds()
        Gets Strings containing the identifiers of Propertys present on the older but not the newer Item.
        Returns:
        See above, but note that identifiers are not returned for Propertys in removed PropertyGroups, or in removed Cards.
